  "description": "Changes the icons of the effects in the game",
  "body": "![Effect Icon+](https://github.com/Arcdashckr/Effect-Icon-Plus/blob/materials/page_art/title/effect_%C4%B1con_plus_title_horizontal.png?raw=true)\n</br> <center> \n<img src=\"https://github.com/Arcdashckr/Effect-Icon-Plus/blob/materials/page_art/display/effect_display_vanilla.png?raw=true\"> </br>\n\n**Changes the icons of the effects in the game** </br>\n**Add a different atmosphere to your gameplay with a more vibrant, more colorful look** </br> </br>\n\n### NEW _1.21.11_ Effect Icons ADDED! </br> </br>\n\n### Mod Compatibility\n\n**<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/excessive-building\" target=\"_blank\">Excessive Building</a>**,\n**<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/wilder-wild\" target=\"_blank\">Wilder Wild</a>**,\n**<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/aether\" target=\"_blank\">The Aether</a>**</br>\n**<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/alexs-mobs\" target=\"_blank\">Alex's Mobs</a>**,\n**<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/alexs-caves\" target=\"_blank\">Alex's Caves</a>**,\n**<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/artifacts\" target=\"_blank\">Artifacts</a>**</br>\n**<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/farmers-delight-refabricated\" target=\"_blank\">Farmer's Delight</a>**,\n**<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/betterend\" target=\"_blank\">BetterEnd</a>**,\n**<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/quark\" target=\"_blank\">Quark</a>**\n\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Arcdashckr/Effect-Icon-Plus/blob/materials/page_art/display/effect_display_mod.png?raw=true\"> </br>\n\n**Request mod compatibility from <a href=\"https://github.com/Arcdashckr/Effect-Icon-Plus/issues\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>** </br> </br>\n\n**Thanks to <a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/upgrade-effect-icon/\" target=\"_blank\">Upgrade Effect Icon</a> by <a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/cherryrero/\" target=\"_blank\">CherryRero</a>**\n</center>\n",
